description:
There’s a Dandy in every universe, and Space Dandy is about to meet them all! He just needs to pull the nearest Cosmic String, and he’ll find himself face-to-face with himself. Talk about trippy!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: I Can`t Be the Only One, Baby
Je ne peux pas être le seul, baby
Only One ni Narenai Jan yo
オンリーワンになれないじゃんよ
